<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Học bài: Giới thiệu React</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
    }

    .main-layout {
      display: flex;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Left - Video Area */
    .video-section {
      flex: 2;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: inset -1px 0 0 #ddd;
    }

    .video-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      background-color: #000;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .video-wrapper iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
    }

    .lesson-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .lesson-description {
      color: #555;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* Right - Sidebar Lessons */
    .sidebar {
      flex: 1;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .sidebar h3 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #007bff;
    }

    .lesson-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .lesson-group h4 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .lesson-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .lesson-list li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .lesson-list a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .lesson-list a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .active {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #28a745;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="main-layout">
    <div class="video-section">
      <div class="video-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dGcsHMXbSOA" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
      <h2 class="lesson-title">1. Giới thiệu React</h2>
      <p class="lesson-description">Trong bài học này, bạn sẽ hiểu React là gì và vì sao nên học React.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar">
      <h3>Danh sách bài học</h3>

      <div class="lesson-group">
        <h4>React cơ bản</h4>
        <ul class="lesson-list">
          <li><a href="#" class="active">1. Giới thiệu React</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">2. JSX và Component</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lesson-group">
        <h4>React nâng cao</h4>
        <ul class="lesson-list">
          <li><a href="#">1. Hook useState</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">2. Hook useEffect</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
